               <msContents>
                  <summary>Canticle of the Flower, ማሕሌተ፡ ጽጌ፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="2r" to="83v" facs="003"/><title type="complete" ref="LIT1834Mahlet"/>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">ጽጌ ፡ አስተርአየ ፡ ሠሪፆ ፡ እም ፡ አፅሙ ፡
                  ለዘአምኃኪ ፡ ጽጌ ፡ ለገብርኤል ፡ ምስለ ፡ ሰላሙ ፡
                  ወበእንተዝ ፡ ማርያም ፡ ሶበ ፡ ኃወዘኒ ፡ መዓዛ ፡ ጣዕሙ ፡
                  ለተአምርኪ ፡ ጽጌ ፡ አሃሊ ፡ እሙ ፡
                  ማኅሌተ ፡ ጽጌ ፡ ዘይሰመይ ፡ ስሙ ፡
                  </incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>(<locus target="#4r #4v #5r #5v" facs="005 006 007"/> are written in a different hand on an inserted leaf), arranged for the days of the week. In each case a piece of thread has been sewn into the upper fore edge.
                </note>
